title: Going the Distance with Duran Cigars and Jack Torano
itunes:title: Going the Distance with Duran Cigars and Jack Torano
description: This weekend we welcome our friend Jack Torano back to The Cigar Authority as we smoke the first cigar in the December Care Package... The Roberto Duran Signature... We will catch up with Jack find out how 2015 was for Duran Cigars and what 2016 will hold...Also Dave returns from Art Basel in Miami and lets us know about that event and his rubbing elbows with various manufactures in the 305...All that and the usual shennanigans on The Cigar Authority...﻿
